campaign contributions
don't affect yours.

1608
01:20:09,004 --> 01:20:10,028
Ohh.

1609
01:20:12,007 --> 01:20:15,238
Senators, Mr. Naylor is not here
to testify on the goings-on

1610
01:20:15,344 --> 01:20:17,141
of the Academy of Tobacco Studies.

1611
01:20:17,246 --> 01:20:19,305
We're here to examine
the possibility

1612
01:20:19,415 --> 01:20:20,814
of a warning logo on cigarettes.

1613
01:20:20,916 --> 01:20:21,883
Now, Mr. Naylor,

1614
01:20:21,984 --> 01:20:23,508
I have to ask you,
out of formality,

1615
01:20:23,619 --> 01:20:25,587
do you believe that smoking
cigarettes, over time,

1616
01:20:25,688 --> 01:20:28,919
