other respiratory conditions

1617
01:20:29,024 --> 01:20:30,218
such as emphysema?

1618
01:20:32,094 --> 01:20:33,584
Yes.

1619
01:20:36,432 --> 01:20:37,330
In fact, I think you'd be
hard-pressed

1620
