- Mr. Naylor.

1624
01:20:44,640 --> 01:20:47,768
There's no need for theatrics.

1625
01:20:47,877 --> 01:20:50,437
Sir, I just don't see the point in a warning
label for something people already know.

1626
01:20:50,546 --> 01:20:51,843
The warning symbol

1627
01:20:51,947 --> 01:20:55,576
is a reminder, a reminder of the
dangers of smoking cigarettes.

1628
01:20:55,684 --> 01:20:57,515
Well, if we want to remind
people of danger,

1629
01:20:57,620 --> 01:20:59,144
why don't we slap
a skull and crossbones

1630
01:20:59,255 --> 01:21:00,222
on all Boeing airplanes,

1631
01:21:00,322 --> 01:21:01,755
Senator Lothridge?

1632
01:21:01,857 --> 01:21:02,789
And all Fords, Senator Dupree?

1633
01:21:02,892 --> 01:21:05,224
That is ridiculous.

1634
01:21:05,327 --> 01:21:07,625
The death toll from airline
and automobile accidents

1635
01:21:07,730 --> 01:21:09,789
doesn't even skim the surface
of cigarettes.

1636
01:21:09,899 --> 01:21:10,957
They don't even compare.

1637
01:21:11,066 --> 01:21:13,125
Oh, this from a senator
who calls Vermont home.

1638
01:21:13,235 --> 01:21:15,362
I don't follow you, Mr. Naylor.

1639
01:21:15,471 --> 01:21:17,132
Well, the real

1640
01:21:17,239 --> 01:21:19,799
demonstrated number one killer
in America is cholesterol,

1641
01:21:19,909 --> 01:21:20,898
and here comes
Senator Finistirre,

1642
01:21:21,010 --> 01:21:23,240
whose fine state is,
I regret to say,

1643
01:21:23,345 --> 01:21:26,371
clogging the nation's arteries
with Vermont cheddar cheese.

1644
01:21:28,017 --> 01:21:30,747
If we want to talk numbers,
how about the millions of people

1645
01:21:30,853 --> 01:21:31,820
dying of heart attacks.

1646
01:21:31,921 --> 01:21:33,183
Perhaps Vermont cheddar

1647
01:21:33,289 --> 01:21:35,655
should come
with a skull and crossbones.

1648
01:21:35,758 --> 01:21:37,589
That is lud...

1649
