1651
01:21:40,429 --> 01:21:41,396
Mr. Naylor,

1652
01:21:41,497 --> 01:21:42,987
we are here to discuss cigarettes.

1653
01:21:43,098 --> 01:21:46,727
Not planes, not cars- cigarettes.

1654
01:21:46,835 --> 01:21:49,497
Now, as we discussed earlier,
these warning labels

1655
01:21:49,605 --> 01:21:52,802
are not for those who know, but
rather for those who don't know.

1656
01:21:54,777 --> 01:21:56,768
What about the children?

1657
01:21:56,879 --> 01:21:58,904
Gentlemen...

1658
01:21:59,014 --> 01:22:00,948
it's called education.

1659
01:22:01,050 --> 01:22:02,915
It doesn't come off the side
of a cigarette carton.

1660
01:22:03,018 --> 01:22:04,076
It comes from our teachers,

1661
01:22:04,186 --> 01:22:06,245
and more importantly, our parents.

1662
01:22:06,355 --> 01:22:09,483
It is the job
of every parent

1663
01:22:09,592 --> 01:22:13,221
to warn their children of all
the dangers of the world,

1664
01:22:13,329 --> 01:22:15,889
including cigarettes, so that
one day, when they get older,

1665
01:22:15,998 --> 01:22:17,829
they can choose for themselves.

1666
01:22:20,069 --> 01:22:23,232
I look at my... son

1667
01:22:23,339 --> 01:22:24,738
who...

1668
01:22:24,840 --> 01:22:26,671
