to come with me today,

1669
01:22:26,775 --> 01:22:29,266
and I can't help but think

1670
01:22:29,378 --> 01:22:31,642
that I am responsible
for his growth

1671
01:22:31,747 --> 01:22:33,874
and his development.

1672
01:22:33,983 --> 01:22:35,507
And I'm proud of that.

1673
01:22:35,618 --> 01:22:36,880
Well, having
said that,

1674
01:22:36,986 --> 01:22:39,546
would you condone him smoking?

1675
