Well, of course not.
He's not 18.

1676
01:22:42,091 --> 01:22:43,149
That would be illegal.

1677
01:22:44,426 --> 01:22:46,519
Yes, I-I heard you deliver
that line on 20-20,

1678
01:22:46,629 --> 01:22:47,994
